Also check the rubber fuel supply, fuel return, and fuel rail hoses 
that connect the injectors in the engine compartment.  If they are 
still original they need to be replaced unless you want the van to go 
up in flames one day.

I recently had a cracked rubber line above #3 cylinder that was 
spewing fuel.  You could smell it everywhere.  Not good...


